{"tid":1621030,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"蒙面法要嚇退既係和理非，和理非一係從此分道揚鑣，一係從此唇齒相依，永不分離","createTime":"2019-10-04T12:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:38:48.000Z","uid":42691,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a66c40cae17ed4f17e187dd22915101293e565","tid":1621030,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:08:31.000Z","msg":"從前有對好兄弟叫<br />\n一個叫阿和 一個叫阿勇<br />\n五年前佢地屋企俾人搞<br />\n兄弟䦧於牆 <br />\n冇抵抗外敵之餘 仲內訌<br />\n<br />\n五年後佢地頭家當然散咗<br />\n但第二次屋企俾人搞<br />\n佢地終於學識兄弟同心 <br />\n知道大家可以互補不足<br />\n阿和多朋友<br />\n阿勇夠打得<br />\n<br />\n但呢次敵人都學精咗<br />\n開下戰書 <br />\n講到明 只係搞阿勇一個 <br />\n只要阿和聽話唔幫手<br />\n就唔會有事<br />\n<br />\n你係阿和 <br />\n請用行動話我知<br />\n你會唔會同阿勇分道揚鑣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唇齒相依 永不分離<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />從此分道揚鑣"},{"pid":"86a2bc38c334497d52826caf63ca957c68d4c840","tid":1621030,"uid":141270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:14:20.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2d153347d3c21b77671a59abfaa4da2d553c896e","tid":1621030,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48aa787a800ef3016e79129759004aef079b5bab","tid":1621030,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />退無可退"},{"pid":"942c2e6295ed91be1385c10ed876e245af924dc4","tid":1621030,"uid":199050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"屌話俾非會員知先有用"},{"pid":"42d4f31fb6ac616ca4e233c6e15a42ba9d6beb5c","tid":1621030,"uid":115045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s